The Shed - Season 1, Episode 2




Marketing Geniuses

When Mama Shed's misfired marketing idea leads to an unplanned ribs giveaway, Brad decides he can do a better job. Brooke disagrees, and challenges Brad and Daddy-O to a guys versus girls Shed marketing contest! The girls struggle to create a Shed calendar (which puts Hazel in a very sticky situation), while the guys invent the one and only "Pig-a-Pult" to launch sandwiches into the sky. Not to be outdone, the Shed Pimps come up with their own marketing scheme... which, conveniently for them, revolves around setting up a kissing booth they promote on social media.




Original Air Date: 05-Aug-2013
